import { Container, Cover, LinkImage, Intro, Title, Extra, Folder, Desc, Arrow } from './styleComps'
import TagComp from '../../components/TagComp';

import folderIcon from '../../assets/folder.svg';
import timeIcon from '../../assets/time.svg';
import likeIcon from '../../assets/like.svg';
import viewIcon from '../../assets/view.svg';


function Card(props) {
    return (<Container odd={props.odd}>
        <Cover>
            <LinkImage href="/" src="https://static.yancey.app/como-usar-imagens-webp-no-wordpress.jpg?x-oss-process=image/format,webp" alt=""/>
        </Cover>
        <Intro>
            <TagComp src={timeIcon}>Released At 2020-07-21 16:20:10</TagComp>
            <Title>WebP 全方位能力检测</Title>
            <Extra>
                <Folder><TagComp src={folderIcon}>javascript</TagComp></Folder>
                <TagComp src={likeIcon}>180 PV</TagComp>
                <TagComp src={viewIcon}>17 likes</TagComp>
            </Extra>
            <Desc>
                WebP 作为当今性价比最高的图片格式之一, 广泛应用于 Web 应用, 无论是电商网站还是图片流网站, 都能看到它的身影. 但它仍不被某些浏览器所支持, 这篇文章通过三种方案, 帮你全方位, 帮你全方位扫清 WebP 能力检测.扫清 WebP 能力检测.
            </Desc>
            <Arrow href="/" />
        </Intro>
    </Container>)
}

export default Card;
